---
title: Chicken Korma Curry & Garlic Rice with Yoghurt, Parsley & Onion Chutney
description: There's nothing like mildly-spiced korma curry topped with onion chutney for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the
fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious curry sauce!
